name: CalorieBurnCalculator
0:
”Alexa open calorie calculator”
”how many calories did I burn if I jump roped for 15 minutes”
”how many calories did i burn if I did 30 pushups”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: calorie calculator
des: Each exercise is dependent on different factors. For some exercises, you will have to specify the distance, the distance unit, as well as duration. For some of them, like pushups, you only need to specify how many you did. Once you tell Alexa your exercise following the format of the utterance, Alexa will tell you how many calories you burned.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
